            <title>[PIG-2797] Tests should not create their own file URIs through string concatenation, should use Util.generateURI instead</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-2797</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;A number of pig tests create URIs via string concatenation when they are trying to load files with something like:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;commandString = &quot;load file:&quot; + fileName + &quot; using &quot;...&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This should just use the Util method generateURI to create the URI correctly in a cross-platform context.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
